José  Maria Alapont





José  Maria Alapont, Retired President & Chief Executive Officer, Federal-Mogul Corporation


José Maria Alapont, 65, is a retired President and Chief Executive Officer of Federal-Mogul Corporation, an automotive and industrial equipment supplier headquartered in Southfield, MI. Mr. Alapont is a former Chief Executive Officer and Director of Fiat Iveco, S.p.A. Prior to joining Fiat Iveco, Mr. Alapont held executive positions of increasing responsibility at Delphi Corporation, Valeo S.A., and Ford Motor Company.A member of Manitowoc’s board since 2016, Mr. Alapont is a member of the Davos World Economic Forum and currently serves as a director of Hinduja Automotive Limited.










